snippet.title: Budget Cuts Ultimate - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
The essential VR stealth action gaming experience that combines the complete Budget Cuts 1 and Budget Cuts 2 games into one seamless adventure! 

In Budget Cuts Ultimate, players must zip, sneak, and stab their way through enemy-filled offices, trains, warehouses, and skyscrapers to take down the evil cost-cutting robots at TransCorp. Is humanity being optimized out of existence altogether? 

Budget Cuts Ultimate is available June 1st 2023, coming to both PS VR2 and Meta Quest 2!

Get the game here: 

PS VR2: https://store.playstation.com/concept/10005325
Meta Quest 2: https://www.oculus.com/experiences/quest/3011203712298006/ 

Join the official discord at https://discord.com/invite/neatcorp
